Title: Final score, Maryland Terrapin men's basketball (75) vs Duke (77), Cole Field House
Description: The Diamondback Photo Morgue consists of images taken for the primary University of Maryland student newspaper, The Diamondback. Photographers took multiple shots at various campus events, athletic games, and of general campus life. Some images were printed in the newspaper, others were kept on file. This collection covers the period from the early 1970s to the late 1990s.
